    // foruser.html
    "foruser_title": "For Users",
    "foruser_tagline": "“Everything saved is everything earned!”",
    "foruser_intro": "Daily purchases are an integral part of our lives, and it’s important that each one is as rational as possible. Our service brings together offers from hundreds of companies, providing access to promotions, discounts, and favorable terms. Choose wisely, save effectively, and get the most value from every purchase!",
    "foruser_marketplace_title": "Nadis – Smart Shopping!",
    "foruser_marketplace_text": "We’re excited to introduce the Nadis marketplace, a platform where you can access thousands of products and services in one place! Everything you need is just a tap away! We’ve developed mobile apps for iOS and Android. We’ve curated a comprehensive list of products neatly sorted by category. You can track promotions, discounts, and news in real-time, plus so much more! Make informed choices easier with honest reviews from real buyers—only they can rate and comment on companies and products on our platform.",
