    "foruser_how_to_start_title": "How to Get Started?",
    "foruser_step_1": "Download the Nadis app",
    "foruser_step_2": "Register",
    "foruser_step_3": "Pay the subscription fee",
    "foruser_step_4": "Log in and start using",
    "foruser_subscription_cost": "Subscription cost: 17,000 ₸",
    "foruser_make_popular_title": "Let’s make Nadis the most popular marketplace in Kazakhstan!",
    "foruser_make_popular_text": "We value mutual support and are confident that together we can achieve more! Our goal is to become the #1 marketplace in Kazakhstan, and we know it’s possible with your help! Tell your friends about Nadis—let them discover great deals and a convenient platform! To make your recommendation both rewarding and valuable, we’ve created a special bonus program. Share your unique referral code and earn cashback rewards by inviting new users to the Nadis platform!",
    "foruser_bonus_program_title": "How to Join the Bonus Program?",
    "foruser_bonus_program_text": "Upon registering on the Nadis platform, you can receive a cashback reward for every new user you invite through a five-tier system. Your first cashback reward comes from the five users you invite who use your unique promo code. Then, each of those five users can invite new users with their own promo codes, and you’ll earn a reward of 1,400 tenge for each one they bring in, up to the fifth tier! You’ll receive push notifications and instant cashback in the app when new users register. Your network can grow up to 3,905 people, earning you a total of 5,467,000 tenge. Every user who joins after you can earn the same reward by building their own five-tier network. Here’s how it works:",
